title: Jeffery Pritchett
text:
Jeffery Pritchett
I am the host of The Church of Mabus radio show. Where we cover politics and metaphysical and paranormal subjects. Also the articles I share range from politics to spirituality to paranormal. A wide gamut of subjects shared from myself and a network of passionate individuals I know from the radio show circuit. Thanks for stopping by.
